@page "/terms"

<PageTitle>Terms & Conditions — Izale Sparkle</PageTitle>

<SeoMeta Title="Terms and Conditions | Izale Sparkle"
         Description="Read the Terms and Conditions for Izale Sparkle including orders, bank transfer payments, returns, refunds, jewellery care, and delivery policies." />

<div class="page-hero" style="min-height:30vh">
    <span class="page-hero-tag">✦ Legal ✦</span>
    <h1 class="page-hero-title">Terms & <em>Conditions</em></h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">Last updated: May 2026</p>
</div>

<section class="terms-section">
    <div class="terms-content">

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>1. General</h2>
            <p>
                Izale Sparkle ("we", "us", "our") operates this website. By accessing or purchasing from our website,
                you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. We reserve the right to update these terms at any time.
            </p>
            <p>
                These terms do not affect your statutory rights under UK consumer law.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>2. Products & Pricing</h2>
            <p>
                We specialise in Indian jewellery, including selected anti-tarnish jewellery pieces.
                All prices are listed in GBP (£) and include VAT where applicable.
            </p>

            <p>
                Anti-tarnish jewellery is designed to resist tarnishing for longer under normal use and care,
                but no jewellery is completely tarnish-proof.
            </p>

            <p>
                We reserve the right to modify prices without notice.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>3. Product Images & AI Processing</h2>

            <p>
                Some product images displayed on this website may be enhanced, edited, or processed using
                artificial intelligence (AI) tools for background removal, lighting improvement, image clarity,
                or presentation purposes.
            </p>

            <p>
                We aim to ensure all product images accurately represent the jewellery items as closely as possible.
                However, slight differences in colour, texture, or appearance may occur due to screen settings,
                lighting, handmade finishes, or AI-assisted image enhancement.
            </p>

            <p>
                Customers may request actual unedited product photographs before purchasing by contacting us.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>4. Orders & Payment</h2>

            <p>
                Orders are subject to acceptance and availability.
            </p>

            <p>
                We currently do not use an online payment gateway.
                Payment must be made by bank transfer only.
            </p>

            <p>
                After checkout, customers will receive a separate email containing bank transfer payment details.
                Orders are only confirmed and processed once payment has been received and cleared.
            </p>

            <p>
                We reserve the right to cancel any order at our discretion.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>5. Delivery</h2>

            <p>
                UK delivery options and pricing are displayed during checkout.
                Delivery times are estimates only and may vary depending on courier services or circumstances outside our control.
            </p>

            <p>
                Ownership and responsibility for the goods pass to the customer upon successful delivery.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>6. Returns & Refunds</h2>

            <p>
                Customers may request a return and full refund for damaged items within 28 days of delivery.
            </p>

            <p>
                Proof of damage is required and must include clear photographs or videos of:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>The damaged item</li>
                <li>The packaging</li>
                <li>Any visible delivery damage</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                Once approved, a 100% refund will be issued via bank transfer.
            </p>

            <p>
                For hygiene reasons, earrings and pierced jewellery may not be eligible for return unless faulty or damaged.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>7. Jewellery Care</h2>

            <p>
                To maintain the quality and finish of your jewellery:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Avoid exposure to water, perfumes, lotions, and chemicals</li>
                <li>Remove jewellery before bathing, swimming, or exercising</li>
                <li>Store jewellery in a cool, dry place</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                Improper care may reduce the lifespan of anti-tarnish coatings and is not considered a manufacturing fault.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>

            <p>
                All content on this website, including text, product images, logos, branding, and designs,
                is the property of Izale Sparkle and may not be copied, reproduced, or used without written permission.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>9. Liability</h2>

            <p>
                Our liability is limited to the purchase price of the products purchased.
                We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of our website or products.
            </p>

            <p>
                Nothing in these terms excludes liability that cannot legally be excluded under UK law.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>

            <p>
                These Terms & Conditions are governed by the laws of England and Wales.
                Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-card">
            <h2>11. Contact</h2>

            <p>
                For questions regarding these Terms & Conditions, orders, or returns, please contact us:
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top:.5rem">
                <strong>Email:</strong> hello@izalesparkle.com<br />
                <strong>Address:</strong> 45 Ryecroft, Haywards Heath, RH16 4NW, United Kingdom
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

